en_148763_0	School students and daily commuters for employment have been badly affected by the ongoing protest by private bus and three-wheeler unions.
en_148763_1	Sri Lanka Transport Board (SLTB) buses are deployed to curb the issue.
en_148763_2	A large number of commuters are crowding at Kandy railway station to take the train as alternate transport.
en_148763_3	Meanwhile, a SLTB bus on Trincomalee- Kandy route was hurled with stones last night.
en_148763_4	Police said the incident took place near the public cemetery in Trincomalee.
en_148763_5	The bus sustained damages but commuters managed to escape without injuries.
